Date:   Sat Mar 21 20:22:46 2026 +0100

    fix: materialize scanline — complementary clip_y for wireframe/solid
    
    Old: wireframe hid bottom-up (clip_y_max 1→0), solid revealed top-down
    (clip_y_max 0→1). This created a gap — no scanline boundary.
    
    New: scanline sweeps top→bottom. Above the line = solid (clip_y_max=scan),
    below the line = wireframe (clip_y_min=scan). Both meet at the scan edge.
    
    Also removed redundant clip_y_min reset in the scan phase that was
    overwriting the scanline position.
    
