    fix: boot-scene flag for sidecar hello message
    
    The hardcoded scene ID check in engine_io.rs ("intro-cpu-on") never
    matched the actual scene ID ("05.intro.cpu-on") after scene IDs were
    standardized. This meant the C# sidecar always received boot_scene=false
    in the hello handshake, causing it to skip MinixBootSequence entirely
    and jump straight to the login prompt.
    
